events.summary: A cherry-colored season: Investigate a new subspecies!
events.description: From Monday, October 9, at 9:00 a.m. until Sunday, October 15, at 4:00 p.m., Pink Rathian will appear in low numbers in Forest Habitats. Pink Rathian will appear as long as you have unlocked Rathian hunts (by completing Chapter 9). While appearance rates are boosted between Friday, October 13, and Sunday, October 15, in Forest Habitats, Rathian will appear more frequently than usual and Pink Rathian will also be easier to find.
